[section#exec.run.loop.ctor
    [:en] Constructor and destructor
    [:zh_CN] 构造函数与析构函数
]

[%@lib@ctor run_loop]
[codeblock:declaration]
run_loop() noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:ensures]
[:en] The [`run_loop] instance[=']s count is 0 and its state is starting.
[:zh_CN] 该 [`run_loop] 实例的计数为 0 且其状态为“启动中”。
[div:end]

[%@lib@dtor run_loop]
[codeblock:declaration]
~run_loop();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] If the [`run_loop] instance[=']s count is not 0 or if its state is running,
invokes [`terminate] ([#except.terminate]).
[:zh_CN] 如果该 [`run_loop] 实例的计数不为 0 或其状态为“运行中”，
则调用 [`terminate] ([#except.terminate])。

[:en] Otherwise, has no effects.
[:zh_CN] 否则，没有任何效果。
[div:end]
